{"data":[{"name":"94:1","price":"Bukankah Kami telah melapangkan untukmu dadamu?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6091,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"alam nashraḥ laka ṣadraka ","translations":["Have not","We expanded","for you","your breast","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","nashraḥ","laka","ṣadraka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,750],[2,750,1500],[3,1500,1960],[4,1960,3515]]}},{"name":"94:2","price":"dan Kami telah menghilangkan darimu bebanmu1585,","arabic":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6092,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1585.  Yang dimaksud dengan \"beban\" di sini ialah kesusahan-kesusahan yang diderita Nabi Muhammad Ṣallallāhu ʻAlaihi wa Sallam dalam menyampaikan risalah.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wawaḍaʿnā ʿanka wiz'raka ","translations":["And We removed","from you","your burden","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wawaḍaʿnā","ʿanka","wiz'raka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2970],[3,2970,4315]]}},{"name":"94:3","price":"yang memberatkan punggungmu?","arabic":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6093,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī anqaḍa ẓahraka ","translations":["Which","weighed upon","your back","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","anqaḍa","ẓahraka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2700],[2,2700,4140],[3,4140,5465]]}},{"name":"94:4","price":"Dan Kami tinggikan bagimu sebutan (nama)mu1586.","arabic":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6094,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1586.  \"Meninggikan nama Nabi Muhammad Ṣallallāhu ʻAlaihi wa Sallam\" di sini maksudnya ialah meninggikan derajat dan mengikutkan namanya dengan nama Allah Subḥānahu wa Ta‘ālā dalam kalimat syahadat, menjadikan taat kepada nabi termasuk taat kepada Allah Subḥānahu wa Ta‘ālā, dan lain-lain.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"warafaʿnā laka dhik'raka ","translations":["And We raised high","for you","your reputation","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["warafaʿnā","laka","dhik'raka",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,1830],[3,1830,3465]]}},{"name":"94:5","price":"Karena sesungguhnya sesudah kesulitan itu ada kemudahan,","arabic":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6095,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-inna maʿa al-ʿus'ri yus'ran ","translations":["So indeed","with","the hardship","(is) ease","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-inna","maʿa","al-ʿus'ri","yus'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2010],[3,2010,2850],[4,2850,4445]]}},{"name":"94:6","price":"sesungguhnya sesudah kesulitan itu ada kemudahan.","arabic":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6096,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"inna maʿa al-ʿus'ri yus'ran ","translations":["Indeed","with","the hardship","(is) ease","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","maʿa","al-ʿus'ri","yus'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1400],[2,1400,1780],[3,1780,2650],[4,2650,4125]]}},{"name":"94:7","price":"Maka apabila kamu telah selesai (dari sesuatu urusan), kerjakanlah dengan sungguh-sungguh (urusan) yang lain1587,","arabic":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6097,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1587.  Maksudnya sebagian ahli tafsir menafsirkan apabila kamu (Muhammad Ṣallallāhu ʻAlaihi wa Sallam) telah selesai berdakwah, maka beribadahlah kepada Allah Subḥānahu wa Ta‘ālā; apabila kamu telah selesai mengerjakan urusan dunia, maka kerjakanlah urusan akhirat dan ada lagi yang mengatakan apabila telah selesai mengerjakan salat, maka berdoalah.","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā faraghta fa-inṣab ","translations":["So when","you have finished","then labor hard","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","faraghta","fa-inṣab",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1730],[3,1730,3565]]}},{"name":"94:8","price":"dan hanya kepada Tuhan-mulah hendaknya kamu berharap.","arabic":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6098,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā rabbika fa-ir'ghab ","translations":["And to","your Lord","turn your attention","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","rabbika","fa-ir'ghab",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1740],[3,1740,4125]]}}],"chapter":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh","Chapter Ash-Sharh","Sharh","Surah Sharh","Chapter Sharh","Ash Sharh","Surah Ash Sharh","Chapter Ash Sharh","Surah 94","Chapter 94","The Relief","الشرح"],"version":{"key":"indonesian_complex","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"id","version":"1.0.0","last_update":1524085200,"title":"Indonesian Translation - King Fahd Complex","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Indonesian by approved Committee by Indonesian Ministry of Islamic Affairs. Corrected by supervision of Rowwad Translation Center. The original translation is available for suggestions, continuous evaluation and development."}}